               <provenance>Ḫāyla Śǝllāse is mentioned as the donor and
                     commissioner of the Ms. in the colophon, together with “his father” Gabra
                     Māryām. His name is also written in the supplication formulas (18rb l.21, 20ra ls.3-4, 20va ls.5-6, 27vb l.19); in
                     the supplication formula on 20ra (ls.4-5) Takla
                     Hāymānot is mentioned as “his son”.</provenance></history>
